<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Background Verification</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .secure-badge { background: #e8f5e9; color: #2e7d32; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .btn-back { background: #ccc; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; color: black; border-radius: 4px; float: left;}
        .btn-next { background: #4CAF50; padding: 10px 20px; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 4px; float: right; cursor: pointer;}
        .nav-buttons { margin-top: 30px; overflow: auto; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Safety Verification</h1>
    <p>Step <%= step %> of <%= totalSteps %>: Identity Check</p>

    <div class="secure-badge">
        ðŸ”’ <strong>256-bit Encryption:</strong> Your data is securely hashed and sent directly to our background check provider.
    </div>

    <form action="/background-gather" method="POST">
        <label for="dob">Date of Birth</label>
        <input type="date" id="dob" name="dob" required style="width: 100%; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px;">

        <label for="ssn">Social Security Number (9 digits)</label>
        <input type="password" id="ssn" name="ssn" placeholder="XXX-XX-XXXX" required style="width: 100%; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px;">

        <label style="display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 10px; margin-top: 20px;">
            <input type="checkbox" name="consent" value="true" required>
            <span>I consent to a background check (Criminal & Eviction history) as per the Fair Credit Reporting Act (FCRA).</span>
        </label>

        <div class="nav-buttons">
            <button type="button" class="btn-back" onclick="history.back()">Back</button>
            <button type="submit" class="btn-next">Continue to Payment</button>
        </div>
    </form>
</body>
</html>